        class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
          Every Project Is Custom
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
          I don't believe in one-size-fits-all pricing. Let's discuss your needs
          and I'll create a custom quote that fits your budget and timeline.
        </p>
        <Button
          variant="dark"
          size="lg"
          href="/services/request?service=brand-logo-design">
          Get Your Custom Quote
        </Button>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Why Choose Me Section -->
  <Section background="white">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
          Why Work With Me?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          You get the quality of a design agency with the speed and
          affordability of working directly with a designer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Benefit 1 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <Zap class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Fast Turnaround</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            Most projects completed in 2-4 weeks, not months. Perfect for
            businesses that need to move quickly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefit 2 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <Target class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
            Small Business Focus
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            I understand small business budgets and timelines. Great value
            without compromising quality.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefit 3 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
