          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            Work directly with me throughout the entire process—no account
            managers or middlemen.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefit 4 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <Lightbulb class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
            Strategic Thinking
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            Not just pretty designs—thoughtful branding that reflects your
            business values and goals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefit 5 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <FileText class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
            All Files Included
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            You get every format you need and full ownership rights. Use your
            brand however you want.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefit 6 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <Sparkles class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Quality Focused</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            2-3 strong concepts, not 20 mediocre options. Quality over quantity,
            every time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <Section
    background="light"
    pattern={{ type: "topography", visibility: "subtle" }}>
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
          Simple, Collaborative Process
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          From initial conversation to final files in just a few steps.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                1
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 pt-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                Discovery Call
              </h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                We discuss your business, target audience, competitors, and
                design preferences. I'll ask questions to understand what makes
                your business unique.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                2
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 pt-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                Research & Concepts
              </h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                I research your industry, competitors, and design trends. Then
                create 2-3 initial logo concepts for you to review.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="shrink-0">
